      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal use-error analysis not required at MRL 2 for Class II device with medium model influence.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2 with medium model influence, a formal use-error assessment is not required. Simulation inputs were reviewed by a second analyst and boundary conditions were verified against the experimental test protocol. No systematic use errors were identified during peer review."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
