      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model-form uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2; qualitative justification of turbulence model selection is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model was selected based on its established performance for rotating machinery with adverse pressure gradients. Literature precedent for centrifugal blood pump CFD supports this choice. Formal model-form uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2 and is therefore not assessed."
    },
    {
