      "acceptanceCriteria": "Input parameter uncertainty propagation not required at MRL 2 beyond boundary condition specification.",
      "rationale": "Inlet flow rate, rotational speed, and fluid viscosity were specified from calibrated measurement sources with documented uncertainty. Formal sensitivity analysis of all model inputs is not required at MRL 2. Boundary conditions are traceable to calibrated instruments with NIST-traceable standards."
