      "acceptanceCriteria": "Statistical characterization of test sample variability not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Three replicate hemolysis measurements were performed at each operating point to assess repeatability. Coefficient of variation was below 8% across all replicates, indicating acceptable repeatability. Formal statistical sample-size analysis is not required at MRL 2 and is therefore not assessed."
